00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:00,000
Atif's a bit strange.

268
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:00,000
If he cares so much about my marriage, why did he send his wife away?

269
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:00,000
You can be whatever you want...

270
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:00,000
But you'll have to do just as I say.

271
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:00,000
That's why I'm here, Atif.

272
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:00,000
Good.

273
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:00,000
I can take you to heights you've never even dreamt of.

274
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:00,000
Magazine covers, fashion shoots, films, dramas - you name it. You'll have it.

275
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:00,000
