451
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:00,000
What's your problem? If you said anything of the sort again, I'll forget you're my friend!

452
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:00,000
Splendid...

453
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:00,000
Hammer some sense into him!

