00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:00,000
Just look at him! So much for friendship!

455
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:00,000
We try to talk some sense into him, but he has a problem with it!
-Just don't say anything then! You always mess everything up!

456
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:00,000
He's our friend!

457
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:00,000
He's got trouble coming his way if he doesn't listen!

458
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:00,000
Jeez, mate, calm down!

459
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:00,000
He's realised he was wrong to hide his reality from Malika.

460
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:00,000
Just give him some time to fix it.

